22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Perils%20of%20Patriarchy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08120415%2Fimages-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Satyajit%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMahanagar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(The%20Big%20City)%2C%20the%20male%20protagonist%2C%20who%20is%20reluctant%20to%20let%20his%20wife%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20as%20a%20sales-girl%2C%20tells%20her%20one%20day%20that%20the%20place%20for%20a%20woman%20is%20at%20home.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20he%20is%20dominating%20or%20a%20misogynist.%20But%20he%20is%20essentially%20insecure%20with%20a%20fragile%20male-ego.%20He%20is%20wary%20of%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20steady%20increments%20and%20appreciations%20that%20she%20had%20earned%20for%20herself%20at%20her%20work%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admits%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20were%20a%20little%20less%20attractive%2C%20then%20I%20could%20have%20allowed%20you%20to%20work.%20If%20beautiful%20women%20like%20you%20go%20out%20to%20work%2C%20men%20get%20distracted%20and%20their%20output%20reduces.%20A%20woman%E2%80%99s%20place%20it%20at%20home.%20I%20am%20a%20staunch%20conservative%20in%20this%20matter.%E2%80%9D%20The%20growing%20confidence%20and%20newfound%20independence%20of%20his%20wife%20unsettles%20him%20%E2%80%93%20all%20the%20more%20when%20he%20becomes%20unemployed%20unexpectedly.%20The%20fear%20of%20losing%20control%20over%20women%20is%20a%20pressing%20patriarchal%20concern%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20big%20the%20city%20is%20or%20how%20small.%20Manifestations%20of%20patriarchy%20need%20not%20always%20be%20brute%20or%20arrogant%20though%2C%20as%20we%20may%20have%20seen%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fanimal-sandeep-reddy-vangas-crude-and-beastly-assault-on-sense-and-sensibility%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Patriarchy%20can%20also%20operate%20in%20polite%20and%20gentlemanly%20ways%20to%20subjugate%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20home%20of%20women%20in%20the%20world%20of%20men%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatriarchy%2C%20for%20long%2C%20has%20been%20preoccupied%20with%20assigning%20the%20%E2%80%98right%E2%80%99%20places%20to%20women.%20It%20has%20presumed%20and%20operated%20with%20this%20principle%20of%20the%20inner-outer%20binary%20of%20places.%20The%20outer%20and%20the%20material%20domain%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98world%E2%80%99%20belongs%20to%20men.%20And%20the%20inner%20domestic%20space%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20female%20sphere%2C%20as%20designated%20by%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20modern%20patriarchal%20imposition%2C%20which%20is%20premised%20on%20the%20convenient%20separation%20of%20work%20and%20domesticity%2C%20which%20is%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20urban-industrial%20order.%20It%20is%20a%20patriarchal%20ploy%20to%20confine%20women%20within%20the%20domesticated%20boundaries%20of%20home%20%E2%80%93%20or%20let%20her%20step%20out%20only%20for%20a%20while%20with%20a%20definitive%20purpose.%20Being%20%E2%80%98out%20there%E2%80%99%20idly%20and%20casually%20is%20predominantly%20a%20male%20prerogative.%20This%20is%20a%20restrictive%20strategy%20to%20define%20and%20limit%20women%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20and%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAwarding%20the%20appropriate%20and%20punishing%20the%20inappropriate%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20decades%20may%20have%20witnessed%20enhanced%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20workforce.%20Women%20have%20stepped%20out%20to%20work%20to%20meet%20the%20financial%20requirements%20of%20family.%20Women%2C%20in%20the%20city%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20increasingly%20become%20financially%20independent.%20The%20social%20acceptance%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20employment%20has%20expanded.%20Her%20presence%20in%20public%20places%20is%20no%20longer%20considered%20to%20be%20transgressional.%20But%20can%20we%20say%20that%20men%20no%20longer%20decide%20what%20constitutes%20the%20right%20time%2C%20right%20place%2C%20right%20attire%20for%20women%20to%20be%20in%20public%3F%20Are%20men%20comfortable%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20women%20going%20out%20without%20a%20reason%2C%20at%20any%20time%20of%20the%20day%20or%20night%3F%20Has%20patriarchy%20stopped%20imposing%20how%20long%20a%20woman%20deserves%20to%20stay%20out%20and%20for%20what%20purpose%3F%20How%20she%20should%20behave%3F%20What%20she%20should%20ideally%20wear%20and%20when%3F%20How%20much%20she%20should%20cover%3F%20How%20much%20of%20exposure%20is%20appropriate%3F%20What%20sort%20of%20revelation%20hurts%20the%20standards%20of%20decency%20imposed%20by%20men%3F%20The%20acceptable%20limits%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20presence%20and%20absence%3B%20women%E2%80%99s%20visibility%20and%20invisibility%3B%20women%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20or%20the%20lack%20of%20it%2C%20are%20authoritatively%20regulated%20by%20men%20even%20now.%20That%20regulation%20is%20instructed%20through%20constant%20appreciation%20and%20condemnation%20of%20certain%20appearances%2C%20beauty-norms%2C%20mannerisms%2C%20postures%2C%20etiquettes%20and%20behavioural%20traits.%20Female%20desire%20is%20disciplined%20by%20making%20the%20inappropriate%2C%20socially%20punishable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20can%20be%20objectified%2C%20sexualised%2C%20tortured%2C%20tormented%20to%20serve%20patriarchal%20interests.%20It%20can%20be%20revealed%20or%20covered-up%E2%80%94depending%20upon%20what%20the%20man%20desires.%20It%20can%20be%20purposefully%20be%20purified%20or%20polluted%3B%20procreated%20or%20pacified%3B%20plundered%20or%20accorded%20to%20suit%20the%20patriarchal%20script.%20It%20is%20a%20narrative%20that%20is%20wrapped-up%20with%20the%20rigid%20yet%20delicate%20patriarchal%20foil%20of%20morality%20that%20has%20dehumanised%20women%20for%20centuries%20by%20stating%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20happens%20to%20her%2C%20she%20must%20have%20called%20it%20upon%20herself.%20She%20must%20have%20been%20in%20the%20wrong%20place%2C%20at%20the%20wrong%20hour%2C%20in%20an%20improper%20manner%2C%20in%20an%20unsuitable%20attire.%20Hence%2C%20she%20deserved%20the%20act%20by%20men%20wrecked%20on%20her.%20She%20deserved%20to%20be%20punished.%20And%20during%20any%20such%20circumstance%2C%20it%20is%20the%20prerogative%20of%20men%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20protect%20her%20or%20to%20abandon%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20owns%20the%20resources%20and%20who%20gets%20to%20decide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20education%2C%20her%20health%2C%20her%20nutrition%2C%20her%20sexuality%2C%20her%20desire%2C%20her%20ambitions%E2%80%94how%20much%20of%20all%20these%20are%20under%20her%20own%20control%3F%20Who%20decides%20for%20how%20long%20she%20can%20study%20and%20to%20what%20extent%20before%20getting%20married%3F%20How%20often%20she%20gets%20to%20decide%20her%20career-options%20and%20nurture%20her%20aspirations%20to%20advance%20in%20her%20field%20of%20interest%3F%20Who%20decides%20whether%20or%20not%20she%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20after%20marriage%3F%20Is%20it%20not%20true%20that%20men%20get%20promoted%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20male-merit%2C%20while%20women%20must%20have%20slept%20her%20way%20up%20the%20ladder%3F%20Aren%E2%80%99t%20our%20households%20full%20of%20examples%20of%20women%20sacrificing%20their%20careers%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20nurturing%20kids%20or%20to%20support%20the%20career-advancement%20of%20their%20spouses%3F%20Who%20follows%20the%20husband%20when%20he%20is%20transferred%3F%20Whose%20purpose%20does%20procreation%20serve%20in%20a%20patrilineal%20mode%20of%20property-transfer%E2%80%94%20father%20to%20his%20legitimate%20sons%3F%20Who%20is%20denied%20property-rights%2C%20so%20often%3F%20Who%20cooks%2C%20and%20who%20gets%20to%20decide%20what%20should%20be%20cooked%3F%20Who%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20household%20duties%2C%20and%20who%20has%20the%20control%20over%20household%20resources%20in%20most%20families%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccept%20everything%2C%20expect%20nothing%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answers%20to%20all%20these%20questions%20are%20so%20obvious%20that%20they%20can%20be%20only%20used%20to%20remind%20our%20patriarchal%20selves%20about%20the%20absolute%20nature%20of%20obedience-production.%20In%20patriarchal%20scheme-of-things%2C%20the%20task%20of%20women%20is%20to%20follow%20orders%20without%20expecting%20any%20reward%20and%20recognition.%20It%20is%20to%20remain%20at%20the%20receiving%20end.%20Gendered%20division%20of%20labor%20has%20a%20deep%20association%20with%20unjust%20performance%20and%20execution%20of%20gendered%20roles.%20That%20glorified%20everyday-performance%20is%20full%20of%20enduring%20pain%2C%20neglect%2C%20indifference%20and%20injustice%2C%20while%20the%20woman%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20compassionate%20and%20benevolent.%20She%20has%20been%20taught%20to%20internalise%20the%20obligation%20of%20remaining%20hungry%20to%20feed%20to%20the%20men%20in%20the%20family.%20She%20has%20to%20be%20the%20sacrificial%20mother%2C%20sister%2C%20daughter%2C%20wife%20and%20girl-friend%20who%20never%20cribs%2C%20complains%20and%20demands.%20She%20has%20to%20bear%20the%20burden%20of%20obedience%20with%20immense%20display%20of%20effeminate%20affection%20and%20tenderness.%20Men%20will%20assert.%20Women%20will%20accept.%20After%20so%20much%20of%20adherence%2C%20unpaid%20service%2C%20if%20men%20choose%20to%20be%20promiscuous%E2%80%94it%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20their%20masculinity%2C%20virility%20and%20macho-pride.%20But%20if%20women%20wish%20to%20look%20elsewhere%2C%20she%20must%20be%20a%20slut%E2%80%94a%20loose-character%20a%20source%20of%20immense%20disrepute%E2%80%94adulteress%20and%20disloyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESusheel%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EBaazaru%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94domesticating%20one%3B%20objectifying%20another%3B%20using%20both%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20lies%20the%20harsh%20truth%20of%20patriarchal%20prejudice%3A%20a%20woman%20who%20dares%20to%20defy%20patriarchy%20is%20a%20great%20source%20of%20fear%20and%20insecurity.%20Unmarried%20women%2C%20the%20widow%20and%20the%20prostitute%20cause%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20patriarchal%20anxiety.%20These%20three%20categories%20of%20women%20are%20not%20necessarily%20under%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20control.%20They%20can%20exercise%20agency%20to%20a%20larger%20extent.%20Her%20body%20and%20sexuality%2C%20if%20not%20owned%2C%20controlled%20and%20tamed%20by%20men%2C%20can%20explode%20anytime.%20It%20reeks%20of%20indecent%20exposure.%20Which%20however%20is%20fine%20when%20sellable%20and%20manipulable%20through%20item-numbers%2C%20pornography%20and%20prostitution.%20All%20of%20which%20are%20domains%20of%20obscenity%20that%20men%20love%20to%20publicly%20condemn%20and%20privately%20consume.%20Patriarchy%20thrives%20on%20the%20binary%20of%20%3Cem%3Esusheel%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebaazaru%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94domesticating%20the%20former%20and%20objectifying%20the%20latter%3B%20and%20using%20both%20on%20different%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENormalise%20oppression%3B%20nullify%20resistance%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20sublime%20reality%20of%20the%20patriarchal%20project%3A%20it%20makes%20women%20its%20biggest%20collaborator%20and%20supporter%20in%20order%20to%20complete%20the%20cycle%20of%20dominance.%20It%20makes%20women%20accept%20oppressive%20everyday%20practices%20through%20the%20normalisation%20of%20oppression%20itself.%20And%20once%20oppression%20is%20internalised%20and%20normalised%2C%20it%20nullifies%20or%20blunts%20the%20possibility%20of%20resistance.%20The%20oppressed%20starts%20to%20accept%20suffering%20as%20a%20legitimate%20fate.%20To%20live%20with%20abuse%2C%20appears%20like%20a%20necessary%20adjustment%20and%20a%20much-needed%20compromise.%20Marital%20rape%20no%20longer%20seems%20like%20a%20violent%20act%20but%20morally-correct%20male%20entitlement%2C%20when%20violence%20is%20internalised.%20Docility%20becomes%20a%20pre-condition%20through%20patriarchal%20conditioning.%20Unpaid%20and%20unrecognised%20domestic%20labor%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20so%20unjust%20any%20longer%2C%20when%20abuse%20is%20embodied.%20A%20release%20from%20such%20a%20suffocating%20condition%20also%20seems%20unnecessary%3B%20so%20does%20a%20corrective%20remedial%20measure.%20Conflict%20gets%20to%20be%20cancelled%3B%20justice%E2%80%94perennially%20deferred.%20And%20right%20to%20remission%E2%80%94reserved%20by%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDispel%20the%20lipstick%20and%20disapprove%20the%20choice%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20return%20to%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMahanagar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20Big%20City)%2C%20where%20the%20female%20protagonist%E2%80%99s%20new-found%20love%20for%20lipstick%20symbolises%20her%20growing%20freedom%20and%20access%20to%20new%20material-conditions%20due%20to%20her%20economic%20independence.%20Lipstick%20is%20positioned%20as%20a%20material-sign%20of%20individualistic%20choice.%20And%20more%20importantly%20that%20choice%20is%20soon%20ridiculed%20by%20her%20husband%20who%20dislikes%20its%20use%20on%20her.%20The%20lipstick%20has%20to%20be%20hidden%20from%20her%20husband%20and%20other%20in-laws%20to%20avoid%20any%20misunderstanding.%20As%20a%20flirtatious%20object%20of%20fashion-indulgence%2C%20it%20can%20only%20be%20applied%20only%20after%20reaching%20office.%20And%20its%20traces%20haves%20to%20be%20wiped-off%20before%20stepping%20inside%20home.%20As%20she%20makes%20hesitant%20strides%20towards%20assertion%20of%20choice%2C%20she%20also%20has%20to%20remain%20considerate%20not%20to%20hurt%20the%20traditional%20sentiments%20of%20men%20at%20home.%20Lipstick%20is%20a%20definitive%20sign%20of%20westernisation%2C%20female%20assertion%20and%20outwardness.%20Once%20it%20is%20discovered%20by%20the%20unemployed%20husband%2C%20he%20does%20not%20hesitate%20to%20immediately%20register%20his%20disapproval%20and%20angst%20with%20its%20usage.%20The%20wife%20throws%20the%20lipstick%20out%20of%20the%20window%20in%20disgust.%20This%20inner%20compulsion%20to%20dispose%20off%20a%20commodity%2C%20not%20only%20indicates%20the%20weightage%20of%20patriarchal%20censure%2C%20but%20also%20expresses%20the%20inhibited%20relationship%20that%20women%20are%20forced%20to%20have%20with%20enhanced%20independence%20and%20indulgence.%20The%20forced%20dispelling%20and%20disposal%20of%20the%20lipstick%20connotes%20how%20women%E2%80%99s%20choices%20are%20governed%2C%20monitored%2C%20resented%2C%20and%20if%20needed%2C%20co-opted%20to%20prevent%20the%20feminine-flight.%20Making%20women%20to%20ultimately%20succumb%20may%20have%20multiple%20patriarchal%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESreedeep%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20Sociologist%20with%20Shiv%20Nadar%20University%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EConsumerist%20Encounters%20(2020).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709879703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08120415%2Fimages-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fthe-perils-of-patriarchy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manifestations%20of%20patriarchy%20need%20not%20always%20be%20brute%20or%20arrogant.%20Patriarchy%20can%20also%20operate%20in%20polite%20and%20gentlemanly%20ways%20to%20subjugate%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fthe-perils-of-patriarchy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20against%20China's%20unfair%20practices%2C%20revitalising%20ties%20with%20India%3A%20Biden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709879702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108319923%2Cimgsize-870289.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-state-of-union-address-us-presidential-election-india-us-ties-china-unfair-prac