most%20any%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmediately%20after%20our%20independence%2C%20we%20experienced%20aggression%2C%20an%20effort%20to%20change%20our%20boundaries%20and%20even%20today%20parts%20of%20India%20are%20occupied%20by%20another%20country%20but%20we%20did%20not%20see%20the%20world%20respond%20saying%2C%20oh%2C%20there's%20a%20great%20principle%20involved%20and%20therefore%2C%20let%20us%20all%20go%20with%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20are%20being%20told%20that%20there%20are%20principles%20involved.%20I%20wish%20I'd%20seen%20that%20principle%20in%20play%20for%20the%20last%2080%20years.%20I've%20seen%20those%20principles%20cherry-picked%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20injustice%20was%20done%20to%20us.%20I'm%20not%20advocating%20it%20should%20be%20done%20to%20everybody%20else.%20We%20have%20been%20very%20clear.%20My%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20stood%20next%20to%20President%20Putin%20and%20said%20we%20want%20to%20see%20the%20end%20to%20this%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709879520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ff2dbrch4_s-jaishankar-ani_625x300_07_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fglobal-south-believes-in-india-china-does-not-participate-s-jaishankar-5198919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Highlighting%20India's%20leadership%20among%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20125%20countries%20of%20the%20platform%20placed%20their%20trust%20in%20India%20and%20that%20China%20skipped%20the%20two%20meetings%20convened%20last%20year%20to%20listen%20to%20their%20concerns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%2