ge.%20It%20also%20strongly%20resonates%20with%20the%20theme%20of%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-womens-day-president-droupadi-murmu-says-lets-remove-remaining-hurdles-from-path-of-young-women-5198299%5C%22%3EInternational%20Women's%20Day%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20'Invest%20in%20women%3A%20Accelerate%20progress'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20of%20India's%20grassroots%20governance%20has%20been%20shaped%20by%20the%2073rd%20and%2074th%20constitutional%20amendments%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explainer-what-is-womens-reservation-bill-4402338%5C%22%3Ereserved%20one-third%20of%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fwomen-s-day-special-we-hub-india-s-first-and-only-start-up-hub-for-women-767282%5C%22%3Ewomen%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%5C%22%3Elocal%20administrative%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20then%2C%2021%20states%20have%20gone%20a%20step%20further%20and%20ensured%2050%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20local%20governance.%20Today%2C%20with%20over%201.4%20million%20elected%20women%20representatives%20(EWRs)%20or%20sarpanchs%2C%20India%20is%20part%20of%20a%20cohort%20of%2020%20countries%20where%20women%20hold%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20local%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrema%20Devi%20Meena%2C%20a%2048-year-old%20woman%20sarpanch%20from%20Kodai%20Gram%20Panchayat%2C%20Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20exemplifies%20this%20progress.%20Through%20her%20leadership%2C%20she%20has%20spearheaded%20vital%20infrastructure%20improvements%2C%20focusing%20on%20enhancing%20road%20conditions%2C%20ensuring%20access%20to%20clean%20toilets%20for%20women%2C%20and%20bolstering%20school%20safety%20for%20girls.%20Her%20efforts%20epitomise%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fndtv-special-ndtv-24x7%2Fkashmiri-women-on-what-all-changed-in-last-4-years-767246%5C%22%3Ewomen%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20steering%20their%20communities%20towards%20sustainable%20development%20and%20gender%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Impact%20of%20Women's%20Leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20Expert%20Committee%20Report%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj%2C%20highlights%20the%20role%20of%20female%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20gender%20mainstreaming%20in%20strengthening%20community%20engagement%20and%20fostering%20inclusive%20governance.%20Echoing%20this%20sentiment%2C%20research%20by%20Clots-Figueras%2C%20I.%202011%2C%20shows%20that%20women%20leaders%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20disadvantaged%20social%20groups%2C%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20invest%20in%20health%20and%20early%20education.%20Their%20approach%20further%20extends%20to%20advocating%20for%20policies%20that%20advance%20social%20justice%20and%20bolster%20women's%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insights%20from%20a%20comparative%20study%20by%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20R.%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Duflo%2C%20E.%202004%2C%20focusing%20on%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20bring%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20impact%20of%20women's%20leadership%20on%20policy%20formulation.%20Their%20findings%20highlight%20a%20heightened%20focus%20on%20public%20goods%20that%20directly%20address%20women's%20needs%2C%20such%20as%20access%20to%20drinking%20water%20and%20the%20improvement%20of%20road%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20evidence%20also%20points%20to%20the%20influence%20of%20women's%20leadership%20in%20mitigating%20harmful%20practices%20that%20affect%20women%20and%20girls.%20The%20research%20by%20Castilla%2C%202018%2C%20brings%20forward%20how%20the%20presence%20of%20women%20in%20local%20governments%20is%20instrumental%20in%20reducing%20the%20likelihood%20of%20child%20marriage%2C%20postponing%20the%20age%20of%20first%20marriage%2C%20and%20reshaping%20aspirations%20for%20both%20parents%20and%20daughters%20towards%20education%20and%20professional%20ambition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESustaining%20The%20Momentum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolve%20of%20women%20leaders%20to%20effect%20change%20is%20vividly%20displayed%20through%20training%20sessions%20organised%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj.%20They%20articulated%20the%20pressing%20need%20to%20confront%20gender-based%20violence%20and%20share%20strategies%20they%20have%20implemented%20to%20address%20it.%20For%20instance%2C%20Sushumlata%2C%20a%20two-time%20sarpanch%20from%20Gram%20Panchayat%20Dawa%2C%20Bhojpur%20District%2C%20Bihar%2C%20organised%20self-defence%20training%20and%20legal%20literacy%20workshops%20for%20women%20and%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20numerous%20other%20elected%20women%20leaders%20have%20launched%20campaigns%20against%20dowry%20and%20domestic%20violence%20and%20advocated%20for%20the%20celebration%20of%20girl%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20sustain%20and%20amplify%20this%20momentum%2C%20strategic%20interventions%20must%20be%20intensified%3A%20capacity%20building%20of%20elected%20women%20representatives%20(EWRs).%20Many%20EWRs%2C%20particularly%20those%20new%20to%20public%20life%2C%20face%20initial%20challenges.%20Quality%20capacity-building%20programmes%20can%20substantially%20boost%20their%20skills%20and%20confidence%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20function%20independently%20as%20leaders.%20Efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20improve%20training%20quality.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj%20is%20partnering%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20to%20introduce%20leadership%20development%20programmes%20for%20elected%20representatives%20at%20the%20district%20level.%20The%20intent%20is%20to%20gradually%20expand%20such%20initiatives%20to%20the%20Gram%20Panchayat%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargeted%20Interventions%20to%20Promote%20Positive%20Masculinity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrevailing%20gender%20norms%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20EWRs%20to%20manage%20public%20duties%20and%20household%20responsibilities%2C%20which%20include%20a%20disproportionate%20share%20of%20domestic%20and%20care%20work.%20Targeted%20training%20and%20public%20campaigns%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20positive%20masculinity%20can%20help%20create%20an%20environment%20that%20tackles%20gender%20biases%20within%20governance%20and%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20Women-Friendly%20Workspaces%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20indicates%20an%20increasing%20trend%20in%20female%20labour%20force%20participation%20(currently%20recorded%20at%2037%25)%3B%20however%2C%20the%20participation%20remains%20below%20the%20global%20average%2C%20hindered%20by%20gender%20norms%20and%20safety%20concerns.%20Panchayats%20have%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20combating%20these%20challenges%20by%20promoting%20women's%20access%20to%20education%2C%20skilling%2C%20and%20safe%20work%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBridging%20The%20Digital%20Divide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gender-related%20digital%20divide%20among%20EWRs%20hampers%20their%20capacity%20to%20fulfil%20their%20roles%20effectively%20in%20an%20era%20of%20increasing%20digitisation%20in%20governance%20and%20public%20service%20delivery.%20To%20address%20this%20challenge%2C%20tailored%20solutions%2C%20such%20as%20customised%20digital%20literacy%2C%20inclusive%20design%20and%20accessibility%20and%20a%20safe%20digital%20environment%2C%20should%20be%20prioritised%20and%20strengthened.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj%20is%20also%20steering%20initiatives%20to%20promote%20digital%20panchayats%20by%20introducing%20online%20platforms%20for%20panchayat%20planning%20and%20development%2C%20online%20audit%2C%20and%20partnership%20with%20states%20for%20delivery%20of%20online%20public%20services.%20The%20Ministry%20is%20also%20investing%20in%20strengthening%20the%20capacities%20of%20elected%20representatives%2C%20including%20women%20representatives%2C%20in%20digital%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20journey%20in%20fostering%20women's%20leadership%20and%20inclusive%20governance%20holds%20powerful%20lessons%20in%20fast-tracking%20the%20localisation%20of%20SDGs.%20This%20bottom-up%20approach%2C%20championed%20by%20strong%20women%20leaders%2C%20not%20only%20transforms%20Gram%20Panchayats%20but%20lays%20the%20groundwork%20for%20India's%20accelerated%20journey%20towards%20inclusive%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Vivek%20Bharadwaj%20is%20Secretary%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Panchayati%20Raj%2C%20and%20Andrea%20M.%20Wojnar%20is%20UNFPA's%20India%20Representative%2C%20part%20of%20Team%20UN%20in%20India)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709877780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Fnj85cjag_rajasthan-women-generic_625x300_14_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-key-to-fast-track-indias-progress-is-more-women-in-local-bodies-5198821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20journey%20in%20fostering%20women's%20leadership%20holds%20powerful%20lessons%20in%20fast-tracking%20the%20localisation%20of%20Sustainable%20Develpoment%20Goals.%20This%20bottom-up%20approach%20lays%20the%20groundwork%20for%20India's%20accelerated%20journey%20towards%20inclusive%20development.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-key-to-fast-track-indias-progress-is-more-women-in-local-bodies-5198821%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-key-to-fast-track-indias-progress-is-more-women-in-local-bodies-5198821%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22