r%22%3A%22Neha%20Vashist%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frandeep-hooda-swatantra-veer-savarkar-made-me-a-director-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F108318516.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dearness%20Allowance%20Hiked%20By%204%25%3A%20What%20Is%20It%20And%20How%20To%20Calculate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20approved%20a%204%25%20increase%20in%20Dearness%20Allowance%20(DA)%20and%20Dearness%20Relief%20(DR)%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20DA%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20basic%20salary%20for%20central%20government%20employees%20and%20pensioners.%20This%20decision%20also%20includes%20a%2025%25%20increase%20in%20transport%2C%20deputation%2C%20and%20canteen%20allowances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20announced%20by%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%2049.18%20lakh%20central%20government%20employees%20and%2067.95%20lakh%20pensioners.%20Considering%20both%20DA%20and%20DR%20and%20the%20increase%20in%20other%20allowances%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20cost%20the%20exchequer%20an%20estimated%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20for%20January%20and%20February%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20reported%20The%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20revision%2C%20various%20allowances%20such%20as%20Housing%20Rent%20Allowances%20(HRA)%2C%20Children's%20Education%20and%20Transport%20Allowances%2C%20and%20gratuities%20will%20see%20an%20increase%20based%20on%20the%20formula%20recommended%20by%20the%207th%20Pay%20Commission.%20Employees%20and%20pensioners%20will%20receive%20arrears%20for%20January%20and%20February%2C%20along%20with%20the%20revised%20rates%20for%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20in%20DA%20and%20DR%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20-%20Industrial%20Workers%20(CPI-IW)%2C%20occurs%20twice%20a%20year.%20The%20first%20revision%2C%20effective%20from%20January%201%2C%20is%20usually%20announced%20just%20before%20Holi%2C%20with%20the%20second%20revision%2C%20effective%20from%20July%201%2C%20decided%20before%20Durga%20Puja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20did%20not%20confirm%20whether%20the%20DA%20and%20DR%20reaching%2050%25%20would%20trigger%20a%20merger%20into%20the%20basic%20salary%2C%20but%20he%20acknowledged%20that%20other%20allowances%20would%20increase%20with%20this%20revision.%20Similar%20increases%20for%20state%20government%20employees%20are%20anticipated%20following%20this%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20HRA%2C%20the%20country%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20categories%20-%20X%2C%20Y%2C%20and%20Z.%20The%20revised%20rates%20for%20X%2C%20Y%2C%20and%20Z%20categories%20are%20now%2030%25%2C%2020%25%2C%20and%2010%25%2C%20respectively.%20For%20instance%2C%20with%20a%20minimum%20basic%20salary%20of%20Rs%2018%2C000%2C%20the%20new%20HRA%20will%20be%20Rs%205%2C400%2C%20Rs%203%2C600%2C%20and%20Rs%201%2C800%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20DA%20will%20also%20impact%20transport%20allowances%2C%20daily%20allowances%2C%20hostel%20subsidies%20for%20children's%20education%2C%20and%20retirement%20gratuity.%20The%20DA%20reaching%2050%25%20will%20also%20benefit%20Chairpersons%20and%20Members%20of%20select%20regulatory%20bodies%2C%20increasing%20their%20monthly%20remuneration%20by%2025%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20is%20DA%20calculated%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDA%20is%20calculated%20using%20the%20All-India%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20(AICPI)%2C%20which%20tells%20us%20how%20the%20prices%20of%20everyday%20items%20change%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20it%20works%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20AICPI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%20at%20how%20much%20the%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20or%20down%2C%20based%20on%20what%20people%20pay%20for%20groceries%20and%20services.%20The%20Labour%20Ministry%20provides%20this%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPick%20a%20Time%20Period%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Depending%20on%20whether%20you%20work%20for%20the%20Central%20government%20or%20the%20Central%20public%20sector%2C%20choose%20a%20specific%20time%2C%20like%20the%20average%20prices%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%20for%20government%20employees%20or%20the%20last%20three%20months%20for%20public%20sector%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20the%20Math%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Plug%20the%20AICPI%20into%20a%20formula%20to%20calculate%20how%20much%20extra%20money%20you%20should%20get.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDA%20calculation%20for%20central%20government%20employees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDA%25%20%3D%20((Average%20of%20AICPI%20(Base%20Year%20-%202001%3D100)%20for%20the%20past%2012%20months%20-115.76)%2F115.76)%20*100%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20central%20public%20sector%20employees%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDA%25%20%3D%20((Average%20of%20AICPI%20(Base%20Year%20-%202001%3D100)%20for%20the%20past%203%20months%20-126.33)%2F126.33)%20*100%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20percentage%20you%20get%20is%20the%20extra%20amount%20added%20to%20your%20salary%20to%20help%20you%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20higher%20costs%20of%20things%20around%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709877480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F90eeoh7o_money-generic_625x300_12_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fdearness-allowance-hike-centre-announces-dearness-allowance-hike-what-is-it-and-how-to-calculate-5198588%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20approved%20a%204%25%20increase%20in%20Dearness%20Allowance%20(DA)%20and%20Dearness%20Relief%20(DR)%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20DA%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20basic%20salary%20for%20central%20government%20employees%20and%20pensioners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano