a%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20several%20attempts%20to%20silence%20my%20protest%20against%20the%20injustice%20which%20took%20place.%20My%20cart%20%E2%80%98PhD%20pakode%20wali%E2%80%99%20is%20also%20part%20of%20my%20protest%E2%80%A6%20I%20started%20this%20cart%20on%20Sunday%2C%20without%20causing%20any%20inconvenience%20to%20anyone%20at%20gate%20number%204%20of%20the%20Arts%20Faculty%2C%20where%20I%20earlier%20held%20my%20protest%E2%80%A6%20A%20day%20or%20two%20later%2C%20police%20visited%20the%20spot%2C%20asking%20me%20for%20my%20licence%20for%20the%20cart%20and%20threatened%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20premises%E2%80%A6%20I%20could%20have%20been%20served%20a%20notice%20in%20a%20dignified%20manner%2C%20but%20what%20was%20the%20need%20to%20book%20me%20under%20a%20case%20for%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20removed%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20cart%2C%20alleging%20encroachment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sent%20a%20team%20to%20remove%20the%20stall%20as%20it%20was%20impeding%20public%20movement%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fpakode-walis-protest-from-lecture-hall-to-frying-pan-dr-ritu-singhs-fight-against-injustice%2Farticleshow%2F108278839.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Enoted%20that%20Singh%20had%20named%20the%20items%20on%20her%20menu%20as%20markers%20of%20protest%2C%20like%20%E2%80%98jumla%20pakoda%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98special%20recruitment%20drive%20pakoda%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98berozgari%20special%20chai%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20the%20teachers%20and%20students%20to%20see%20the%20plight%20of%20Dalit%20academics%20and%20the%20systemic%20barriers%20they%20face%20even%20after%20graduating%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Delhi%20University%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5