0chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20as%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20person%E2%80%9D%20holding%20a%20seat%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20order%2C%20the%20judge%20makes%20a%20string%20of%20controversial%20and%20debatable%20observations%20%E2%80%93%20from%20praising%20Adityanath%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20to%20blaming%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20by%20political%20parties%20for%20riots%20in%20the%20country%20and%20referring%20to%20his%20own%20record%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20legal%20battle%20and%20threats%20received%20by%20him%20from%20Muslim%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20even%20said%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20order%20should%20be%20sent%20to%20Adityanath%20so%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20could%20take%20action%20against%20those%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20officials%20who%20allegedly%20assisted%20the%20accused%20Muslim%20cleric%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20Khan%20and%20did%20not%20act%20as%20per%20law%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20then%20government%20(UP%20was%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20at%20the%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%2C%20additional%20district%20judge-fast%20track%20court%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20who%20passed%20the%20order%2C%20while%20serving%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20Varanasi%20in%202022%20had%20passed%20controversial%20directions%20regarding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%20Diwakar%2C%20as%20civil%20judge%20senior%20division%2C%20had%20ordered%20the%20sealing%20of%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20mosque%20after%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20claimed%20that%20a%20stone%20found%20in%20the%20ablution%20tank%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshivling%E2%80%9D.%20Judge%20Diwakar%20had%20given%20his%20nod%20to%20videography%20inside%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20by%20a%20court-appointed%20advocate%20commissioner%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20five%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20demanding%20daily%20access%20to%20prayer%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%E2%80%99%20they%20claimed%20was%20located%20outside%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20posted%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%20on%20March%205%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%202010%20Bareilly%20riots%20case%2C%20added%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20and%20summoned%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20March%2011.%20The%20judge%20dubbed%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20a%20prominent%20cleric%20of%20the%20Barelvi%20sect%20and%20president%20of%20the%20political%20party%20Ittehad-e-Millat%20Council%2C%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20mastermind%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%20on%20March%202%2C%202010%20after%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20over%20the%20route%20of%20a%20Muslim%20religious%20procession.%20Several%20persons%20were%20injured%20and%20property%20damaged%20in%20the%20incident.%20A%20curfew%20had%20been%20imposed%20in%20the%20city%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20recording%20the%20statements%20of%20witnesses%2C%20the%20judge%20concluded%20that%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20speech%20to%20a%20gathering%20a%20Muslims%20had%20instigated%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%2C%20who%20was%20posted%20to%20his%20present%20court%20in%20November%202023%2C%20started%20off%20by%20stating%20that%20if%20a%20religious%20person%20occupies%20a%20seat%20of%20power%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20good%20results.%20He%20cited%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20king%E2%80%99%20propounded%20by%20ancient%20Greek%20philosopher%20Plato%20in%20his%20work%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Plato%20had%20said%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20end%20to%20suffering%20in%20the%20Greek%20city%20states%20until%20they%20had%20philosopher%20kings%2C%20said%20Diwakar%20in%20his%20order%20hearing%20the%20Bareilly%20riots%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJustice%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20a%20king%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Diwakar%2C%20quickly%20adding%20that%20though%20in%20the%20present%20times%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98justice%E2%80%99%20was%20used%20in%20the%20legal%20sense%2C%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Plato%20it%20was%20used%20in%20the%20context%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20head%20of%20power%20should%20be%20a%20religious%20person%2C%20because%20the%20life%20of%20a%20religious%20person%20is%20not%20one%20of%20enjoyment%20but%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20dedication.%20An%20example%20of%20this%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%20is%20the%20peethadeshwar%20of%20the%20great%20Siddhapeeth%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%2C%20mahant%20baba%20shri%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20ji%2C%20who%20is%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20has%20proven%20the%20above%20concept%20to%20be%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Judge%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20however%2C%20if%20any%20religious%20person%20acts%20contrary%20to%20the%20aforementioned%2C%20such%20as%20provoking%20people%20of%20this%20community%2C%20then%20law%20and%20order%20gets%20disrupted%20and%20riots%20occur%2C%20said%20the%20judge.%20Diwakar%20said%20an%20example%20of%20this%20was%20Maulana%20Khan.%20The%20judge%20stressed%20that%20since%20Khan%20is%20a%20religious%20leader%20and%20belonged%20to%20the%20Ala%20Hazrat%2C%20the%20main%20dargah%20of%20Bareilly%2C%20which%20has%20great%20recognition%20in%20the%20Muslim%20society%2C%20and%20heads%20the%20IMC%2C%20he%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20influence%20in%20Muslim%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20further%20remarked%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20reason%20for%20riots%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20parties%20here%20are%20engaged%20in%20appeasement%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%E2%80%9D.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20the%20morale%20of%20prominent%20people%20of%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparticular%20religion%E2%80%9D%20increases%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20believe%20that%20even%20if%20they%20cause%20riots%2C%20no%20harm%20will%20fall%20upon%20them%20due%20to%20protection%20provided%20by%20power%2C%20said%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20then%20recalled%20his%20time%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20alleged%20threats%20he%20received%20following%20his%20orders%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter.%20He%20said%20that%20even%20though%20he%20had%20filed%20an%20FIR%20after%20receiving%20a%2032-page%20threat%20from%20a%20Muslim%20outfit%2C%20nobody%20had%20been%20arrested%20till%20date.%20This%20caused%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20a%20civil%20judge%20in%20Shahjahanpur%2C%20to%20worry%20about%20his%20safety%2C%20said%20Diwakar%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20prevailed%20in%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20then%20referred%20to%20the%20alleged%20remarks%20by%20Khan%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20even%20claimed%20that%20had%20UP%20not%20been%20ruled%20by%20Adityanath%2C%20Khan%20would%20have%20recently%20incited%20a%20riot%20in%20Bareilly.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20incident%20of%20stone-pelting%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%20last%20month%20when%20people%20were%20returning%20home%20after%20participating%20in%20a%20jail-bharo%20protest%20organised%20by%20Khan%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20court%20in%20Varanasi%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20to%20Hindus%20for%20prayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20then%20claimed%20that%20ever%20since%20he%20passed%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%2C%20the%20attitude%20of%20people%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cparticular%20religion%E2%80%9D%20and%20officials%20towards%20him%20had%20become%20strange.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20seemed%20that%20I%20had%20committed%20some%20sin%20by%20giving%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20judge%2C%20stressing%20that%20he%20passed%20the%20order%20as%20per%20legal%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20Bareilly%20rioting%20case%2C%20the%20judge%2C%20while%20criticising%20the%20alleged%20inaction%20of%20the%20police%20and%20government%20officials%20in%20failing%20to%20include%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20despite%20there%20being%20sufficient%20evidence%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20noted%20that%20in%20India%2C%20rarely%20has%20the%20mastermind%20of%20a%20riot%20been%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Khan%20had%20been%20arrested%20he%20was%20not%20named%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%20is%20not%20the%20only%20judge%20linked%20to%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid-Kashi%20Vishwanath%20matter%20to%20stir%20a%20controversy.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fajaya-krishna-vishvesha-handed-gyanvapi-cellar-hindus-ombudsman-university-in-lucknow%5C%22%3Efirst%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20retired%20district%20judge%20of%20Varanasi%20Ajaya%20Kumar%20Vishvesha%20who%20had%20on%20January%2031%2C%20his%20last%20working%20day%2C%20controversially%20handed%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20to%20Hindus%20for%20prayers%2C%20was%20recently%20appointed%20an%20ombudsman%20of%20a%20public%20university%20in%20Lucknow.%20Adityanath%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20chief%20minister%2C%20is%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709873057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08101344%2FFcWENqHaQAIDJ0v.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fex-gyanvapi-case-judge-hails-philosopher-king-adityanath-in-order-indicting-muslim-cleric%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20called%20Adityanath%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20person%E2%80%9D%20holding%20a%20seat%20of%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fex-gyanvapi-case-judge-hails-philosopher-king-adityanath-in-order-indicting-muslim-cleric%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20To%20%26quot%3BRevitalise%26quot%3B%20India%20Ties%20Amid%20China's%20%26quot%3BUnfair%20Practices%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Biden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20standing%20up%20against%20China's%20unfair%20economic%20practice%2C%20standing%20up%20for%20peace%20and%20stability%20across%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20and%20revitalising%20its%20partnership%20with%20allies%20like%20India%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20last%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%20before%20the%20November%20election%2C%20Biden%20said%20the%20US%20wants%20competition%20with%20China%2C%20but%20not%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20on%20Thursday%20told%20Americans%20that%20the%20country%20is%20in%20a%20stronger%20position%20to%20win%20the%20competition%20for%20the%2021st%20Century%20against%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20standing%20up%20against%20China's%20unfair%20economic%20practice%2C%20standing%20up%20for%20peace%20and%20stability%20across%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20but%20revitalising%20our%20partnership%20with%20allies%20and%20the%20Pacific%2C%20India.%20Australia%2C%20Japan%2C%20South%20and%20Korea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20years%2C%20all%20I've%20heard%20from%20my%20Republican%20friends%20and%20so%20many%20others%20is%20that%20China's%20on%20the%20rise%20and%20America%20is%20falling%20behind.%20They've%20got%20it%20backwards.%20America%20is%20rising%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20the%20best%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Biden%20said%20in%20his%20third%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20Address%20to%20the%20Congress%20which%20was%20watched%20by%20millions%20of%20Americans%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%