0--%20and%20a%20national%20TV%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%20over%20an%20hour%20long%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20high-stakes%20test%20of%20his%20ability%2C%20at%2081%20and%20making%20history%20as%20the%20oldest%20ever%20US%20president%2C%20to%20think%20on%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20frequently%20booed%20and%20heckled%20Biden%20but%20he%20shot%20back%20each%20time%2C%20sprinkling%20a%20vigorous%20delivery%20with%20jokes%20that%20mocked%20his%20opponents%20for%20everything%20from%20planning%20to%20cut%20billionaires'%20taxes%20to%20refusing%20to%20take%20climate%20change%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20arrived%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Capitol%2C%20crammed%20with%20congressional%20members%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20justices%20and%20government%20leaders%2C%20to%20extended%20cheers%20from%20supporters%20and%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3Bfour%20more%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20multiple%20challenges%20facing%20Biden%20--%20including%20from%20the%20Democratic%20left%20--%20protesters%20against%20his%20support%20for%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Hamas%20tried%20to%20block%20the%20motorcade%20from%20the%20White%20House%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%2077%2C%20has%20a%20narrow%20lead%20over%20Biden%20in%20opinion%20polls.%20However%2C%20he%20faces%20multiple%20criminal%20charges%20linked%20to%20his%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20his%202020%20election%20loss%20and%20refusal%20to%20give%20back%20boxes%20of%20top%20secret%20documents%20after%20grudgingly%20leaving%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Greatest%20comeback'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Biden%20slammed%20Republican%20abortion%20opponents%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20%26quot%3Bno%20clue%20about%20the%20power%20of%20women%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20what%20Democrats%20see%20as%20a%20key%20vote-winning%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20touted%20the%20booming%20US%20econo