t%3BI'm%20ready%20to%20fix%20it.%20Send%20me%20the%20border%20bill%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20light%20of%20age%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20millions%20of%20Americans%20tuning%20in%20to%20the%20spectacle%2C%20much%20of%20the%20interest%20was%20not%20just%20what%20Biden%20said%2C%20but%20how%20he%20sounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%20wanting%20to%20push%20back%20on%20the%20Republican-led%20narrative%20that%20he%20is%20too%20old%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Biden%20responded%20with%20more%20jokes%20--%20and%20said%20that%20age%20had%20given%20him%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it%20may%20not%20look%20like%20it%20but%20I've%20been%20around%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20to%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20you%20get%20to%20be%20my%20age%20certain%20things%20become%20clearer%20than%20ever.%20I%20know%20the%20American%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20tradition%2C%20First%20Lady%20Jill%20Biden%20hosted%20a%20number%20of%20guests%20chosen%20to%20highlight%20the%20White%20House's%20priorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20they%20include%20a%20Texan%20woman%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20state%20for%20an%20abortion%2C%20a%20woman%20whose%20IVF%20treatment%20was%20halted%20by%20an%20Alabama%20court%20ruling%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Sweden%2C%20which%20became%20NATO%20newest%20member%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709870220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3ejabf3_biden_625x300_08_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdemocracy-under-assault-joe-biden-slams-donald-trump-for-bowing-down-to-putin-5198068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%