elieves%20that%20he%20has%20got%20more%20sharper%20with%20better%20game%20awareness%20due%20to%20consistent%20opportunities.%20Having%20made%20his%20debut%20at%20this%20very%20venue%20in%202017%2C%20Kuldeep%20in%20past%20seven%20years%20have%20only%20made%2012%20Test%20appearances%2C%20with%20four%20of%20them%20on%20trot%20in%20the%20current%20series%20against%20England.%20On%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20fifth%20Test%20against%20England%2C%20Kuldeep%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20with%20five%20top-order%20wickets.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20play%20regularly%2C%20you%20get%20more%20confident%20about%20your%20bowling.%20Game%20awareness%20also%20comes%20with%20it.%20It%20is%20very%20important%20to%20keep%20playing%20regularly%20as%20it%20makes%20your%20bowling%20sharp%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2029-year-old%2C%20who%20now%20has%2017%20wickets%20in%20the%20series%20with%20hopefully%20one%20more%20innings%20to%20increase%20his%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChances%20In%20Tests%20were%20sporadic%20in%20past%20few%20years%2C%20then%20there%20was%20dip%20in%20form%20and%20also%20a%20knee%20surgery%20for%20the%20talented%20spinner%2C%20who%20made%20technical%20adjustments%20to%20get%20his%20mojo%20back.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20it%20was%20very%20challenging.%20I%20had%20changed%20my%20action%2C%20it%20took%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20to%20find%20that%20rhythm.%20Now%2C%20things%20are%20all%20set%20and%20I%20am%20enjoying%20it.%20In%20Ranchi%2C%20I%20tried%20something%20with%20my%20run-up%20(faster%20approach%20to%20the%20crease%20as%20it%20was%20a%20slow%20surface)%2C%20and%20I%20practise%20that%20regularly.%26quot%3B%20Kuldeep%20bowled%20a%20highly%20productive%2015-over%20spell%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20lunch%20break%20on%20day%20one%2C%20something%20he%20says%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20do%20of%20late%20purely%20because%20of%20his%20improved%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20knee%20surgery%20in%20September%202021%2C%20Kuldeep%20changed%20his%20fitness%20routine%2C%20increased%20his%20pace%20and%20straightened%20his%20run-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20that%20helped%20India%20bowl%20out%20England%20for%20218%20on%20a%20flat%20track%2C%20Kuldeep%20said%20it%20is%20only%20because%20his%20targeted%20fitness%20regimen%20that%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20make%20those%20changes%20and%20bowl%20long%20spells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBowling%20is%20all%20about%20fitness.%20I%20have%20worked%20a%20lot%20on%20my%20fitness%20in%20the%20last%2018%20months.%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20make%20certain%20changes%20in%20my%20bowling%20because%20of%20improved%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20Kuldeep%20said%20at%20the%20day-end%20media%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20doing%20specific%20things%20on%20my%20fitness%20which%20is%20allowing%20me%20to%20bowl%20long%20spells.%20At%20Rajkot%20(12%20overs%20in%20first%20innings)%20and%20Ranchi%20(14%20overs%20in%20second%20innings)%20also%2C%20I%20bowled%20log%20spells.%20I%20have%20gotten%20used%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%20Kuldeep%20has%20been%20getting%20more%20bite%20from%20flat%20surfaces%20compared%20to%20the%20other%20spinners%20and%20that%20was%20also%20evident%20on%20Thursday%20when%20he%20got%20the%20ball%20to%20drift%20and%20turn%20back%20sharply%20to%20castle%20Zak%20Crawley.%20The%20ball%20turned%20from%20imaginary%20fifth%20off-stump%20and%20ended%20up%20shattering%20the%20England%20opener's%20leg%20stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20using%20the%20drift%20well%20on%20both%20sides.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20get%20them%20out%20for%20218%20as%20it%20is%20a%20good%20wicket.%20As%20a%20spinner%2C%20you%20focus%20on%20the%20length%20and%20try%20to%20hit%20good%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%2C%20you%20change%20plans%20as%20per%20conditions.%20If%20you%20are%20getting%20drift%2C%20then%20you%20have%20to%20think%20about%20the%20lines%20as%20well.%20The%20more%20you%20play%2C%20the%20easier%20it%20becomes%20to%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpeed%20also%20matters.%20If%20you%20bowl%20at%20a%20certain%20speed%20and%20change%20your%20pace%2C%20it%20gets%20difficult%20for%20the%20batters%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20cricketer%20from%20Kanpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharamsala%20is%20a%20special%20venue%20for%20Kuldeep%20as%20he%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20here%20back%20in%202017.%20Following%20a%20successful%20debut%2C%20Kuldeep's%20career%20did%20not%20follow%20an%20upward%20trajectory%20though%20now%20he%20seems%20to%20have%20found%20the%20best%20version%20of%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20interesting%20phase.%20It%20has%20been%20seven%20years%20since%20(debut).%20I%20have%20become%20a%20lot%20more%20mature%20about%20my%20bowling.%20I%20understand%20my%20game%20a%20lot%20better%20now.%20I%20know%20how%20to%20read%20the%20wicket.%26quot%3B%20On%20his%20stellar%20effort%20on%20day%20one%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20wicket%20is%20good.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20to%20break%20considering%20the%20cold%20weather.%20It%20was%20cold%20in%20the%20first%20hour.%20The%20ball%20was%20gripping%20and%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20put%20revs%20on%20the%20ball.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20and%20Ashwin%20shared%20an%20emotional%20moment%20after%20England%20got%20all%20out%20shortly%20after%20tea.%20Considering%20Ashwin%20is%20playing%20his%20100th%20Test%2C%20Kuldeep%20wanted%20him%20to%20keep%20the%20ball%20and%20his%20more%20experienced%20wanted%20the%20other%20way%20round.%20The%20premier%20off-spinner%20cleaned%20up%20with%20the%20tail%20with%20a%20four%20wicket%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20exchange%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAsh%20bhai%20told%20me%20I%20have%2035%20balls%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20keep%20this%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20publish