student-who-lived-with-family-arrested%2Farticleshow%2F108315386.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcanada-mass-stabbing-6-dead-at-ottawa-student-who-lived-with-family-arrested%2Famp_articleshow%2F108315386.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcanada-mass-stabbing-6-dead-at-ottawa-student-who-lived-with-family-arrested%2Famp_articleshow%2F108315386.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDidn't%20Prepare%20Me%20For%20Married%20Life%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashwin's%20Wife%20On%20Early%20'Shock'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20gets%20down%20to%20action%20against%20England%20in%20the%20fifth%20Test%20in%20Dharamsala%2C%20Ashwin%20achieved%20a%20huge%20personal%20milestone.%20The%20match%20is%20Ashwin's%20100th%20for%20the%20Indian%20Test%20team.%20In%2099%20Tests%2C%20Ashwin%20took%20507%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2023.91%2C%20including%2035%20five-wicket%20hauls%2C%20with%20the%20best%20bowling%20figures%20of%207%2F59.%20Combine%20it%20with%20his%20tally%20of%203%2C309%20runs%20in%20140%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2026.14%2C%20with%20five%20centuries%20and%2014%20fifties%20and%20he%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20all-rounders%20of%20the%20modern%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20match%2C%20Ashwin's%20wife%20Prithi%20penned%20an%20honest%20note%20on%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20married%20to%20an%20international%20cricketer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20there%20was%20no%20dating%20in%20our%20pre-marriage%20life%2C%20he%20didn't%20prepare%20me%20for%20married%20life.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20got%20married%2C%20we%20were%20off%20to%20Kolkata%20to%20play%20a%20Test%20the%20next%20day%20against%20the%20West%20Indies.%20I%20wasn't%20aware%20there%20would%20be%20so%20much%20media%20attention.%20I%20remember%20this%20instance%20when%20he%20was%20tying%20the%20wedding%20Thali%20(like%20a%20mangalsutra)%2C%20all%20I%20could%20see%20was%20photographers%20around%20both%20of%20us.%20And%20we%20couldn't%20spot%20the%20one%20we%20had%20hired%20for%20the%20wedding.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20taste%20of%20what%20it%20meant%20to%20be%20around%20a%20cricketer%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Prithi%20Ashwin%20wrote%20in%20a%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fravi-ashwin-journey-to-100-tests-wife-prithi-ind-vs-eng-9197507%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20love%20the%20game%20contributed%20to%20overcoming%20it.%20I%20know%20I%20love%20him%20but%20if%20I%20didn't%20like%20what%20he%20was%20doing%2C%20would%20I%20have%20done%20what%20I'm%20doing%20today%3F%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20problem%20putting%20him%20first.%20But%20I%20was%20very%20unsettled%20the%20first%20few%20years%2C%20not%20in%20the%20marriage%20but%20in%20how%20much%20this%20profession%20was%20taking%20away%20from%20what%20I%20could%20be%20building%20with%20him.%20First%2C%20it%20was%20surprise%2C%20then%20shock%2C%20then%20denial.%20Then%20it%20was%20pure%20misery.%20When%20we%20had%20children%2C%20I%20was%20sacrificing%20all%20our%20time.%20It%20took%20time%20to%20understand%20that%20if%20you%20want%20to%20succeed%20at%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20it%20always%20comes%20at%20a%20cost%2C%20either%20not%20spending%20time%20with%20his%20parents%2C%20or%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20children.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrithi%20went%20on%20to%20the%20explain%20how%20the%20game%20impacted%20Ashwin's%20life%20and%20how%20the%20period%20during%20Covid%20changed%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sport%20took%20over%20his%20life%20from%20the%20time%20he%20was%20seven%20and%20I%20took%20time%20to%20realise%20that%20sometimes%20they%20don't%20know%20anything%20else.%20There%20is%20no%20fuel%20in%20the%20vehicle%20to%20put%20into%20another%20relationship%20or%20another%20presence%20in%20your%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Covid%20that%20really%20got%20us%20together.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20it%20was%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%20because%20we%20all%20suddenly%20realised%20that%20he%20is%20probably%20never%20going%20to%20play%20cricket%20again.%20So%20what%20is%20our%20life%20about%3F%20That's%20probably%20eight-nine%20years%20into%20a%20marriage%20when%20we%20really%20lived%20together%20under%20a%20roof%20like%20a%20normal%20couple%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709867400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-08%2Fr-ashwin-wife_650x400_41471949263.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fhe-didnt-prepare-me-for-married-life-r-ashwins-wife-on-surprise-shock-denial-explains-reason-5187535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20spinner's%20100th%20Test%2C%20R%20Ashwin's%20wife%20Prithi%20penned%20an%20honest%20note%20on%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20married%20to%20a%20international%20cricketer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Boy%20Dies%20After%20Participating%20In%20Dangerous%20Social%20Media%20Challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%2011-year-old%20boy%2C%20Tommie-Lee%20Gracie%20Billington%2C%20lost%20his%20life%20after%20inhaling%20toxic%20chemicals%20in%20a%20social%20media%20challenge%20called%20%26quot%3Bchroming.%26quot%3B%20The%20incident%20occurred%20in%20Lancaster%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETommie-Lee%20was%20at%20a%20friend's%20house%20when%20they%20attempted%20the%20challenge.%20Chroming%20involves%20inhaling%20fume