thian%20Colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EImproved%20higher-ed%20regulations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20targeted%20relief%2C%20McCann%20said%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20helping%20borrowers%20is%20the%20Education%20Department's%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bcolleges%20are%20providing%20value%2C%20and%20that%20education%20pays%20off%20for%20borrowers%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20of%20that%20effort%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-new-gainful-employment-rule-student-loan-debt-relief-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20department's%20new%20gainful%20employment%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E.%20First%20established%20in%202014%2C%20the%20rule%20cut%20off%20federal%20student%20aid%20for%20schools%20that%20offered%20degrees%20that%20left%20students%20with%20too%20much%20debt%20compared%20to%20their%20likely%20post-graduation%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20repealed%20the%20rule%20in%202019%2C%20Biden's%20administration%20reinstated%20it%20to%20protect%20students%20from%20taking%20on%20spiraling%20debt%20loads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20also%20announced%20a%20financial%20transparency%20framework%20to%20give%20students%20upfront%20information%20on%20the%20costs%20of%20their%20degrees%20and%20how%20much%20debt%20they%20should%20expect%20to%20acquire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20new%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoes-debt-ceiling-deal-ban-student-debt-relief-payment-pause-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecodified%20the%20end%20of%20the%20over%20three-year%20student-loan%20payment%20pause%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20bill%20to%20raise%20the%20debt%20ceiling%20in%20June%2C%20leading%20payments%20to%20once%20again%20resume%20in%20October.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20make%20the%20transition%20easier%20for%20borrowers%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20a%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%2C%20known%20as%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-borrowers-apply-income-driven-repayment-save-plan-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintended%20to%20lower%20monthly%20payments%20for%20many%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20includes%20a%20range%20of%20provisions%20intended%20to%20make%20relief%20more%20accessible%20for%20borrowers.%20In%20January%2C%20the%20department%20announced%20it%20would%20be%20implementing%20one%20of%20those%20provisions%20ahead%20of%20schedule%3A%20loan%20forgiveness%20for%20borrowers%20who%20originally%20borrowed%20%2412%2C000%20or%20less%20and%20made%20as%20few%20as%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20department%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-debt-cancellation-save-income-driven-payment-plan-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.2%20billion%20in%20debt%20relief%20for%20153%2C000%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20group%20to%20benefit%20from%20that%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20plan%20elements%20to%20be%20implemented%20later%20this%20year%20include%20cutting%20payments%20for%20undergraduate%20borrowers%20in%20half%20and%20counting%20periods%20spent%20in%20deferment%20or%20forbearance%20toward%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20second%20attempt%20at%20broader%20debt%20relief%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20process%20that%20has%20likely%20gotten%20the%20most%20attention%20from%20borrowers%20is%20the%20Education%20Department's%20second%20attempt%20at%20a%20broader%20version%20of%20student-debt%20cancellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20Biden's%20first%20relief%20attempt%2C%20the%20department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-take-cancel-student-debt-higher-education-act-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C