n%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20348px)%2085vw%2C%20348px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07174024%2F61R1Y4CnhTL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07174024%2F61R1Y4CnhTL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20652w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07174024%2F61R1Y4CnhTL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%20196w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22534%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Welcome%20to%20Paradise%E2%80%99%2C%20Twinkle%20Khanna%2C%20Juggernaut%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20salient%20aspect%20of%20the%20book%20is%20something%20pointed%20out%20by%20%E2%80%93%20of%20all%20people%20%E2%80%93%20her%20husband%2C%20the%20actor%20Akshay%20Kumar.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC05vjHOoaAD%2F%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20video%20clip%20from%20a%20book%20talk%20posted%20to%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20Instagram%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumar%20is%20seen%20asking%20Khanna%20from%20the%20audience%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20main%20characters%20are%20women.%20Does%20this%20mean%20that%20men%20are%20irrelevant%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhanna%E2%80%99s%20storytelling%20is%20subtle%20enough%20to%20skirt%20straightforward%20characterisations%20like%20these.%20Men%20weave%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20five%20stories%20that%20make%20the%20book%20%E2%80%93%20assaulting%20women%2C%20loving%20them%2C%20dying%20on%20them%2C%20and%20meandering.%20Maybe%20they%20are%20good.%20Maybe%20they%20are%20bad.%20But%20they%20are%20not%20the%20focus.%20Kumar%20is%20right.%20Women%20are%20the%20main%20characters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20this%20truth%20Khanna%20delivers%20with%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20tools%20in%20her%20toolkit%20%E2%80%93%20her%20language.%20It%20is%20often%20rich%2C%20but%20a%20long%20way%20from%20stilted.%20In%20dialogues%2C%20when%20expressing%20stray%20thoughts%2C%20for%20detailed%20descriptions%20and%20to%20give%20window%20to%20rituals%20exasperations%2C%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20language%20is%20easy%2C%20clever%20and%20%E2%80%93%20incredibly%20in%20a%20world%20teeming%20with%20writing%20%E2%80%93%20her%20own.%20It%20subsumes%20vernacular%20lilts%20%E2%80%93%20here%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98chalo%E2%80%99%2C%20there%20a%20%E2%80%98quick%20walk-shalk%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20her%20language%20that%20ensures%20that%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20books%20are%20bestsellers%2C%20and%20also%20language%20that%20helps%20her%20tackle%20the%20question%20of%20the%20unavoidable%20politics%20of%20her%20husband.%20Kumar%20is%20a%20supporter%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20has%20been%20vocal%20in%20this%20role.%20Many%20realities%20of%20present-day%20India%20are%20irreconcilable%20with%20rightwing%20thought%2C%20and%20because%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20precedes%20him%2C%20a%20reader%20comes%20to%20Khanna%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20this%20fact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20is%20at%20odds%20with%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20own%20repeated%20and%20careful%20assertions%20that%20her%20political%20views%20differ%20from%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s.%20So%20different%20were%20they%20that%20Modi%20once%20told%20Kumar%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnofrs0alz5o%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einformal%20and%20largely%20panned%20interview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20there%20must%20be%20domestic%20bliss%20considering%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20outrage%20against%20him%20on%20Twitter.%20But%20Khanna%20has%20maintained%20that%20it%20is%20unfeminist%20to%20posit%20her%20as%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20mouthpiece%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20these%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20territory%20is%20distinctly%20tricky.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20readers%20who%20arrive%20at%20the%20last%20story%20%E2%80%98Jelly%20Sweets%E2%80%99%20and%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20about%20a%20Muslim%20family%20can%20be%20goaded%20into%20reading%20it%20with%20a%20clean%20slate.%20And%20yet%20it%20is%20refreshing%20to%20read%20of%20Muslim%20women%20forging%20unconventional%20paths%20for%20themselves%2C%20speaking%20of%20love%20and%20loss%2C%20and%20just%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebeing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20with%20no%20sanctimony%20in%20the%20narrator%E2%80%99s%20voice%2C%20no%20compulsion%20to%20devote%20an%20entire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fmade-in-heaven-polygamy-polygyny-muslims-dia-mirza-himanta-biswa-sarma-reality%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eepisode%20to%20polygamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20indulging%20in%20the%20odd%20Smithian%20sympathy%20we%20feel%20for%20the%20privileged%2C%20you%20feel%20almost%20grateful%20that%20such%20non-motivated%20portrayal%20does%20exist%20and%20that%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20craft%20and%20thought%20went%20into%20it%20from%20a%20person%20who%20could%20have%20perhaps%20got%20away%20without%20both.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20many%20questions%20one%20can%20ask%20about%20what%20a%20short%20story%20is%20supposed%20to%20achieve.%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20latest%20collection%20delivers%20satisfactory%20answers%20to%20almost%20all%20of%20them.%20The%20stories%20are%20gem-like%20in%20length%2C%20they%20end%20leaving%20you%20full%20but%20you%20also%20actively%20wonder%20as%20to%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20characters%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20they%20are%20a%20journey%20through%20the%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20authors%20urge%20less%20successful%20ones%20to%20write%20of%20realities%20most%20known%20to%20them.%20Others%20are%20fantasy%20writers.%20A%20large%20part%20of%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20reality%20is%20for%20us%20to%20see%20because%20she%20is%20almost%20always%20under%20the%20spotlight.%20But%20a%20larger%20part%20seemingly%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20her%20to%20honour%20the%20twilight%20days%20that%20the%20Indian%20woman%20leads%20%E2%80%93%20days%20which%20just%20are%2C%20without%20incident%2C%20without%20noteworthiness%2C%20but%20chock-full%20of%20pain%2C%20anticipation%20and%20happiness.%20Her%20treatment%20of%20time%20is%20perceptive%20and%20something%20that%20allows%20her%20to%20carve%20her%20niche%20among%20writers%20today.%20Most%20of%20the%20stories%20have%20significant%20leaps%20in%20them%20through%20years.%20Most%20also%20speak%20of%20the%20many%20Indias%20we%20have%20lost.%20Most%20honour%20the%20power%20of%20a%20told%20tell%2C%20a%20small%20anecdote%2C%20an%20articulated%20memory.%20The%20story%20%E2%80%98Nearly%20Departed%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20a%20science%20teacher%20who%20taught%20Freddie%20Mercury%20in%20Panchgani%20%E2%80%93%20without%20this%20becoming%20the%20central%20focus%20of%20her%20existence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EWelcome%20to%20Paradise%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20all-around%20celebration%20of%20women%20by%20an%20author%20who%20is%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20best%20way%20possible%20%E2%80%93%20very%20difficult%20to%20ignore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709865025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07174550%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Ftwinkle-khanna-women-welcome-to-paradise-book-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20'Welcome%20to%20Paradise%2C'%20multiple%20dichotomies%20come%20to%20roost.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Ftwinkle-khanna-women-we