tions%20on%20Russia%20partly%20because%20it%20imports%20Russian%20energy%3B%20partly%20because%20the%20ruling%20Fidesz%20party%20of%20President%20Viktor%20Orb%C3%A1n%20admires%20Putin%20and%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20political%20system.%20On%20February%2023%2C%20Hungary%20blocked%20an%20EU%20statement%20pledging%20%E2%80%9Cunwavering%E2%80%9D%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStance%20of%20India%20and%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWestern%20hopes%20that%20authoritarian%20China%2C%20a%20global%20political%20and%20economic%20influence%2C%20and%20India%2C%20a%20(weakening)%20democracy%2C%20both%20major%20buyers%20of%20Russian%20arms%20and%20energy%2C%20would%20use%20their%20influence%20over%20Moscow%20to%20condemn%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20are%20unrealistic.%20China%20and%20India%20were%20among%20the%2035%20countries%20(18%25%20of%20UN%20member-states)%20which%20abstained%20from%20voting%20against%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20annexation%20of%20Eastern%20Ukraine.%20China%E2%80%99s%20neutrality%20is%20easier%20to%20explain%20because%20together%20with%20Russia%2C%20it%20seeks%20to%20end%20America%E2%80%99s%20Asian%20and%20global%20primacy.%20And%20Beijing%20blames%20the%20US%20for%20the%20war.%20India%E2%80%99s%20abstention%20appears%20surprising%2C%20since%20its%20territorial%20integrity%20has%20long%20been%20threatened%20by%20China%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20both%20China%20and%20India%20claim%20to%20be%20upholding%20international%20law%2C%20the%20UN%20Charter%2C%20and%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20states.%20Ironically%2C%20India%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findia-us-cooperation-will-act-as-force-multiplier-for-rules-based-world-order-rajnath%2Farticle67793038.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroutinely%20now%20says%20it%20stands%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98rules%20based