of%20this%20rock%20are%20a%20promising%20place%20to%20look%20for%20hydrogen%20reserves%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20already%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20stretch%20runs%20from%20Kansas%20up%20to%20Ontario%2C%20then%20down%20to%20Michigan.%20The%20other%20is%20offshore%2C%20running%20the%20length%20of%20New%20Jersey%20to%20Georgia%2C%20according%20to%20Ellis.%20USGS%20started%20looking%20for%20these%20reserves%20in%202021%20and%20has%20drilled%20several%20wells%2C%20with%20more%20planned%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllis%20told%20the%20Senate%20committee%20that%20research%20is%20also%20ongoing%20in%20France%20and%20Australia%2C%20and%20active%20exploration%20efforts%20are%20underway%20in%20Brazil%20and%20Colombia.%20In%20February%2C%20researchers%20announced%20they%20had%20discovered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-discover-albanian-mine-could-be-hydrogen-source-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydrogen%20reservoir%20in%20a%20mine%20in%20Albania%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bulqiz%C3%AB%20chromite%20mine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e4c438ce7f1785b2e5c0a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bulqiz%C3%AB%20chromite%20mine%20just%2025%20miles%20east%20of%20Albania's%20capital%20Tirana%20contains%20a%20huge%20reservoir%20of%20hydrogen.%3Cp%3EGENT%20SHKULLAKU%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20exploring%20for%20geologic%20hydrogen%20use%20many%20of%20the%20same%20technologies%20that%20are%20used%20in%20the%20oil%20and%20gas%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Senator%20John%20Barrasso%20(R-WY)%20said%20in%20the%20hearing.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20many%20of%20the%20people%20exploring%20for%20hydrogen%20today%20spent%20their%20careers%20exploring%20for%20oil%20and%20gas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20unclear%20how%20much%2