p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNidhi%20was%20overwhelmed%20and%20wondered%20how%20we%20would%20fulfil%20so%20many%20orders.%20I%20reassured%20her%20that%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20Nidhi%20faced%20initially%20was%20mental%2C%20as%20she%20wondered%20if%20they%20could%20succeed%2C%20and%20build%20a%20business%20from%20home.%20Having%20worked%20in%20a%20corporate%20environment%2C%20she%20worried%20about%20the%20intricacies%20involved%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20from%20scratch%2C%20especially%20one%20that%20is%20very%20laborious%20and%20customer-centric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worried%20if%20this%20hair%20oil%20would%20work%20on%20everyone.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20hair%20fall.%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20doing%20a%20business%20and%20was%20unsure%20of%20facing%20everyting%20that%20it%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20candidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother-in-law%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20a%20rock%20and%20defied%20her%20age%20to%20literally%20burn%20the%20midnight%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20win%20for%20the%20duo%20was%20successfully%20fulfilling%20the%20100%20orders.%20From%20that%20day%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-woman%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20the%20oil.%20Till%20September%202023%2C%20they%20made%20the%20oil%20at%20home%20and%20managed%20manufacturing%2C%20packaging%2C%20customer%20support%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20website%20all%20by%20themselves.%20After%20the%20success%20of%20their%20oil%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20shampoo%20using%20Rajni%E2%80%99s%20recipe%2C%20a%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub%20and%20comb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C