-features%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhone%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20marketplaces%20tantalise%20you%20with%20enticing%20exchange%20offers%2C%20tempting%20you%20to%20upgrade.%20But%20have%20you%20ever%20paused%20to%20consider%20what%20becomes%20of%20your%20old%20phones%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20marketplaces%20and%20stores%20provide%20the%20option%20of%20purchasing%20a%20refurbished%20phone.%20Such%20a%20phone%20undergoes%20thorough%20inspection%20for%20defects%2C%20repairs%2C%20and%20replacement%20of%20faulty%20parts.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3ERedseer%20Strategy%20Consultants%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20refurbished%20or%20used%20smartphone%20market%20in%20India%20is%20projected%20to%20soar%20to%20%2410%20billion%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Avneet%20Singh%20set%20out%20to%20buy%20an%20iPhone%20for%20his%20mother%20but%20found%20the%20new%20phone%E2%80%99s%20price%20beyond%20his%20budget%20when%20he%20visited%20a%20store%20with%20his%20friend%2C%20Saket%20Saurav.%20However%2C%20an%20enterprising%20salesman%20offered%20them%20a%20second-hand%20phone%20at%20a%20significantly%20lower%20price%2C%20nearly%20Rs%2035%2C000%20less%20than%20a%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20tempting%20offer%2C%20the%20phone%20lacked%20any%20checks%20and%20came%20without%20a%20warranty.%20Opting%20against%20the%20risky%20purchase%2C%20Avneet%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20together%20at%20Shopclues%2C%20he%20and%20Saket%20recognised%20a%20problem%20worth%20solving.%20Subsequently%2C%20Shopclues%20introduced%20a%20refurbished%20mobile%20category%2C%20ReNew%2C%20which%20quickly%20generated%20multi-crore%20revenue%20within%20its%20first%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20extensive%20research%20on%20the%20refurbished%20mobile%20market%20and%20spotting%20an%20opportune%20time%20in%20May%202017%2C%20they%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20launched%20ReFit%20Global%20%E2%80%94%20a%20refurbished%20phone%20startup%2C%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20reduce%20e-waste%20by%20recycling%20and%20refurbishing%20second-hand%20gadgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReFit%20is%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%20240%20crore%20this%20financial%20year%20and%20prevent%2055%2C000%20to%2065%2C000%20phones%20from%20becoming%20e-waste%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecycling%20e-waste%2C%20promoting%20a%20circular%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frefit2-1709213840.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ReFit%20bagged%20a%20Rs%202%20crore%20deal%20at%20Shark%20Tank%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frefit2-1709213840.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frefit2-1709213840-300x230.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frefit2-1709213840-500x383.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frefit2-1709213840-768x589.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frefit2-1709213840-150x115.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EReFit%20bagged%20a%20Rs%202%20crore%20deal%20at%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Delhiites%20met%20through%20common%20friends%20and%20their%20friendship%20solidified%20after%20two%20sales%20stints%20together%20at%20LG%20and%20Shopclues.%20The%20aforementioned%20incident%20and%20subsequent%20launch%20of%20the%20ReNew%20portfolio%20at%20Shopclues%20alerted%20the%20two%20MBA%20graduates%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20the%20refurbished%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20conducted%20market%20research%20and%2C%20while%20overseeing%20the%20ReNew%20portfolio%2C%20gained%20practical%20insights%20into%20the%20details%20of%20the%20category.%20They%20learned%20firsthand%20about%20sourcing%20inventory%2C%20refurbishing%20phones%2C%20and%20identifying%20potential%20sales%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20service-class%20backgrounds%2C%20the%20duo%20had%20long-held%20aspirations%20of%20becoming%20entrepreneurs.%20Recognising%20a%20promising%20business%20opportunity%20and%20observing%20a%20significant%20market%20gap%2C%20they%20made%20the%20bold%20decision%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams.%20They%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342247%2Fmangaluru-man-quits-corporate-career-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20behind%20their%20stable%20corporate%20careers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20dive%20headfirst%20into%20the%20world%20of%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20invested%20all%20their%20savings%20and%20the%20then%2028-year-olds%20took%20a%20personal%20loan%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20each%20and%20bootstrapped%20their%20business.%20With%20a%20total%20capital%20of%20Rs%2055%20lakh%2C%20they%20started%20ReFit%20Global%20in%20May%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20refurbished%20market%20was%20just%20picking%20up%20at%20that%20time.%20Up%20until%20then%2C%20we%20only%20had%20the%20option%20to%20buy%20new%20phones%20or%20second-hand%20phones.%20A%20second-hand%20phone%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20credibility.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20offer%20quality%20checked%20and%20tested%20refurbished%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Saket%20(35)%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20ReFit%20Global%2C%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-based%20company%20was%20started%20with%20a%20team%20of%20seven%20including%20the%20two%20founders%2C%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20offline%20market.%20Initially%2C%20Saket%20and%20Avneet%20would%20load%20about%20100%20refurbished%20phones%20in%20their%20cars%2C%20set%20out%20to%20the%20market%2C%20and%20convince%20channel%20partners%20to%20buy%20these%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20visit%20different%20markets%20and%20be%20on%20the%20road%20for%20almost%2010%20days%20at%20a%20time%20in%20the%20initial%20days.%20We%20explained%20the%20product%20to%20the%20channel%20partners%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20trust%20us%20with%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money.%20Educating%20consumers%20and%20partners%20was%20the%20first%2C%20challenging%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avneet%20(35)%2C%20co-founder%20and%20COO%2C%20ReFit%20Global.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20slowly%20found%20a%20few%20channel%20partners%20who%20invested%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%202%20to%205%20lakh%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20the%20business%20of%20the%20enterprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20two%20years%20were%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20sleepless%20nights%20for%20these%20entrepreneurs%2C%20fully%20committed%20to%20their%20venture.%20Saket%20remembers%20that%20at%20the%20start%20of%20their%20business%2C%20his%20wife%20was%20pregnant%2C%20while%20Avneet%E2%80%99s%20parents%20had%20just%20begun%20searching%20for%20a%20bride%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20invested%20all%20our%20savings%3B%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98do%20or%20die%E2%80%99%20for%20us.%20We%20had%20a%20strong%20belief%20that%20it%20would%20work%2C%20and%20worked%20hard.%20We%20took%20no%20days%20off%20and%20burnt%20the%20midnight%20oil.%20We%20focused%20on%20building%20a%20good%20offline%20base%20and%20educating%20our%20distributors%20while%20building%20partnerships%20with%20mobile%20brands%20and%20marketplaces%20to%20buy%20back%20old%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Saket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20paid%20off%20as%20people%20started%20trusting%20their%20brand%20and%20their%20sales%20grew.%20In%20the%20first%20year%20of%20operations%2C%20they%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%208%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%2047-point%20quality%20check%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frefit-1709539888.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20phones%20go%20throw%20a%2047%20point%20quality%20check%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frefit-1709539888.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frefit-1709539888-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frefit-1709539888-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frefit-1709539888-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frefit-1709539888-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343779%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20phones%20go%20through%20a%2047-point%20quality%20check.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReFit%20sources%20old%20phones%20from%20three%20channels%20%E2%80%94%20marketplaces%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart%2C%C2%A0%20mobile%20manufacturers%20like%20Samsung%2C%20Oppo%2C%20Vivo%2C%20and%20Apple%2C%20and%20large%20format%20retailers%20like%20Sangeetha%2C%20Poorvika%2C%20and%20Croma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20phones%20reach%20their%20office%2C%20they%20are%20tested%20using%20ReFit%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20diagnostic%20application%20which%20has%2047%20quality%20check%20parameters.%20Saket%20says%20that%20within%20two%20and%20a%20half%20minutes%2C%20the%20application%20identifies%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20with%20the%20phone.%20Their%20engineers%20then%20rectify%20and%20repair%20the%20phones%2C%20conducting%20further%20checks%20to%20see%20if%20the%20sensors%20and%20cameras%20are%20working%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20faults%20are%20fixed%2C%20the%20application%20is%20run%20again%20to%20check%20if%20it%20passes%20all%20quality%20checks.%20It%20is%20then%20sent%20either%20to%20offline%20partners%20or%20sold%20through%20their%20own%20website%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20in%20October%202023.%20They%20also%20offer%20a%20six-month%20warranty%20on%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20average%20selling%20price%20offline%20is%20Rs%206%2C000%20and%20online%20is%20Rs%2011%2C000.%20There%20is%20more%20demand%20for%20high-end%20phones%20online%2C%20say%20the%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20share%20that%20they%20sell%20between%2055%2C000%20to%2065%2C000%20phones%20every%20month%20and%20have%20sold%20over%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263287%2Fbangalore-global-childrens-peace-award-photograph-kids-mobile-parents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%201.75%20million%20phones%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20date.%20They%20claim%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20profitable%20from%20the%20outset%20and%20have%20achieved%20a%20consistent%20100%20percent%20year-on-year%20growth.%20Their%20revenue%20reached%20Rs%20187%20crore%20last%20year%20and%20is%20projected%20to%20hit%20Rs%20240%20crore%20this%20year.%20Operating%20in%20over%20100%20cities%2C%20they%20have%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20difference%20between%20a%20second-hand%20and%20refurbished%20phone%2C%20explains%20Saket%2C%20is%20the%20quality%20and%20credibility.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20quality%20testing%20or%20checking%20done%20on%20a%20second-hand%20phone.%20We%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20problem%20with%20the%20phone%20and%20give%20you%20a%20warranty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20phones%20are%20also%20beneficial%20for%20the%20environment%20as%20they%20extend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252476%2Fmumbai-e-waste-recycling-discard-dead-laptops-mobile-phones-computer-keyboard-ecoreco-book-my-junk-environment-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifespan%20of%20gadgets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20contributing%20to%20waste.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20Waste%20Electrical%20and%20Electronic%20Equipment%20(WEEE)%20forum%20reported%20that%205.3%20billion%20mobile%20phones%20would%20become%20waste%20in%20that%20year%20alone.%20Instead%20of%20recycling%20old%20phones%2C%20many%20people%20either%20keep%20them%20at%20home%20or%20discard%20them%20in%20bins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20devices%20contain%20valuable%20materials%20like%20gold%2C%20copper%2C%20and%20silver%2C%20which%2C%20if%20recycled%2C%20can%20prevent%20the%20need%20for%20extracting%20precious%20minerals%20and%20help%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReFit%20also%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20and%20secured%20a%20deal%20for%20Rs%202%20crore%20from%20three%20%E2%80%98Sharks%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Anupam%20Mittal%2C%20Vineeta%20Singh%2C%20and%20Amit%20Jain.%20Post%20their%20appearance%20on%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20they%20have%20received%20over%2020%2C000%20queries%20from%20retailers%20and%20distributors%20in%20just%2010%20days%2C%20say%20the%20elated%20founders%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20want%20to%20increase%20their%20online%20presence%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20initially%20keeping%20their%20venture%20a%20secret%20from%20their%20families%20to%20establishing%20a%20company%20valued%20at%20Rs%20200%20crore%2C%20Avneet%20and%20Saket%20exemplify%20the%20power%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340982%2Fiit-delhi-graduates-aroleap-x-fitn