d%20to%20make%20them.%20Also%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300789%2Fretrofitting-how-to-convert-your-old-cars-into-electric-vehicles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicle%3C%2Fa%3E%20(EV)%20consumption%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20too%20heavy%20and%20no%20one%20realised%20that%20this%20sector%20would%20take%20off%20soon.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20whatever%20OEMs%20(original%20equipment%20manufacturers)%20in%20India%20needed%2C%20they%20were%20importing%20those%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20college%20semester%20project%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20build%20Li-ion%20cells%20at%20a%20Rs%20200%20crore%20R%26amp%3BD%20laboratory%20set%20up%20on%20campus.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20ordered%20lithium%20and%20cobalt%20from%20China.%20Due%20to%20various%20reasons%2C%20these%20materials%20didn%E2%80%99t%20arrive%20on%20time%20for%20our%20project.%20To%20complete%20it%2C%20we%20bought%20some%20old%20Li-ion%20cells%20from%20the%20market%2C%20extracted%20whatever%20materials%20we%20could%20in%20very%20impure%20forms%20and%20then%20fabricated%20Li-ion%20cells%20(half%20cells)%20that%20delivered%20some%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20acquire%20these%20materials%20in%20India%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20start%20recycling%20old%20Li-ion%20batteries.%20We%20predicted%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20Li-ion%20batteries%20are%20going%20to%20enter%20the%20country%2C%20and%20if%20we%20recycle%20them%2C%20these%20materials%20can%20be%20reused%20to%20make%20cells.%20See%2C%20you%20can%20recycle%20metals%20like%20lithium%20infinitely.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20BatX%20Energies%20was%20born.%20We%20spent%20the%20following%20semesters%20researching%20what%E2%80%99s%20required%20to%20recycle%20Li-ion%20batteries%20on%20a%20larger%20scale%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image